(71, '_ZtbKAAcNFU', 'paper_reference', 'creative', 'creative', 'narrative', '10.1098/rsta.2013.0164', '10.1098/rsta.2013.0164', 'Episode 4 - Chthonian Planets', 'Quinn and Micky ponder the formation of planets and tell the story of their own wandering world.\n\nFurther reading on the theories mentioned:\n\nBlogging on Chthonian:\nhttps://demystifyingscience.com/blog/is-earth-captured-rogue-chthonian\n\nReferences from the Episode:\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/2003.10314\nhttps://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/abs/2019/03/aa34489-18/aa34489-18.html\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0312384\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/1201.2687\nhttps://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/international-journal-of-astrobiology/article/exchange-of-material-between-solar-systems-by-random-stellar-encounters/298F8D4D53D996C81091BE61B1438BA2\nhttps://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2003Natur.422..143V/abstract\nhttps://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/full/10.1098/rsta.2013.0164\nhttps://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21969736?dopt=Abstract\n\nMore readings from us:\nhttps://demystifyingscience.com\n\nCome talk to us!\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/demystifysci\n\nFacebook:  https://www.facebook.com/demystifysci/\n\nMusic\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\nShilo Delay: \nhttps://soundcloud.com/laterisgone\n\nBlue Dressed Man: \nhttps://blue-dressed-man.bandcamp.com\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~', '2020-04-27 08:49:51', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Demystifying Science', 'UCUfzVdgNu2xLThgM2qQZmSQ', 763, 77, 9, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2020-07-23 02:48:17'),
