(95, 'dqbl9hnm7g4', 'paper_reference', 'fixed', 'fixed', 'no_voice', '10.1109/TII.2014.2299233', '10.1109/TII.2014.2299233', 'Developing Vehicular Data Cloud Services in the IoT Environment   | IEEE | IEEE projects 2014', 'The advances in cloud computing and internet of things (IoT) have provided a promising opportunity to resolve the challenges caused by the increasing transportation issues. We present a novel multilayered vehicular data cloud platform by using cloud computing and IoT technologies. Two innovative vehicular data cloud services, an intelligent parking cloud service and a vehicular data mining cloud service, for vehicle warranty analysis in the IoT environment are also presented. Two modified data mining models for the vehicular data mining cloud service, a Naive Bayes model and a Logistic Regression model, are presented in detail. Challenges and directions for future work are also provided.\nPublished in:\nIndustrial Informatics, IEEE Transactions on  (Volume:10 ,  Issue: 2 )\nDate of Publication:\nMay 2014\n\nPage(s):\n    1587 - 1595 \nISSN :\n    1551-3203 \nINSPEC Accession Number:\n    14267597 \nDOI:\n    10.1109/TII.2014.2299233 \n\nDate of Publication :\n    10 January 2014 \nDate of Current Version :\n    02 May 2014 \nIssue Date :\n    May 2014 \nSponsored by :\n    IEEE Computer Society \nPublisher:\n    IEEE \n\nMob: 9985613074, 7396708351\n\nSite: www.newieeeprojects.com\n\nEmail: newieeeprojects@gmail.com', '2014-09-06 12:58:44', 'IEEE, IEEE projects 2014', NULL, NULL, 'Renown Technologies', 'UC1bqqQAlQgOUm4aN4n3mA4w', 94, 294, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, '2020-07-24 10:00:01');
