(142, 'AaOYo7i13H4', 'paper_reference', 'creative', 'presentation', 'narrative', '10.1016/j.chb.2014.03.003', 'sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0747563214001241', 'Why QUITTING SOCIAL MEDIA is a Good Idea | Science-based', 'Hi there! Do you wanna know why quitting social media is a good idea? You\'ve come to the right place! Quitting social media sounds scary but is SO worth the try. We live in the world of social media and most of the time we can\'t do without it. We need to stay connected. And sometimes maybe just a little too much. Then we get overwhelmed and feel the toxicity of this environment and  sometimes think of quitting social media for good. A little cleanse or fast or a break whatever you may call it never hurt anybody and is worth the try! But why quitting social media is a good idea? I bring to light some of the studies done around using and quitting social media over the years. I hope you find this video useful, as it\'s packed with facts on social media and its negative effects it can have on us. \nWish you a wonderful day! Hopefully wondering why quitting social media is a good idea for you hehe \nLots of love,\nRM\n_________________________________________________________________\nSOURCES: \n Me, my selfie, and I: The relationship between editing and posting selfies and body dissatisfaction in men and women, 2019 \n\nhttps://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1740144518301414?via%3Dihub#bib0010\n\n\n Association between social media use and depression among u.s. young adults, 2017\n\nhttps://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4853817/\n\n Facebooks emotional consequences: Why Facebook causes a decrease in mood and why people still use it., 2014\n\nhttps://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0747563214001241', '2019-04-25 18:08:40', 'why quitting social media is a good idea, quitting social media, quitting social media is a good idea, why quitting social media is good, why quitting social media is good for you, social media, quit social media, why you should quit social media, social media cleanse, social media fast, healthy habits for social media, rosegold mermaid, social media detox', 'en-GB', 'en-GB', 'Rosegold Mermaid', 'UCgb89qZJa9nfGRnzIsRgZmQ', 650, 22, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, '2020-07-25 14:05:43'),
