(172, 'l2aKA2tyhIk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '10.1093/molbev/mst199', 'academic.oup.com/mbe/article/31/1/48/1050570', 'Prokaryo - Remipede [Music Video]', 'Hope that you enjoy learning about the Remipede, a rare and fascinating crustacean that lives deep in saltwater caves throughout the Caribbean. It is completely blind and is also the only known venomous crustacean. You can check out more information about remipedes and remipede venom in the following article:\nvon Reumont et al. 2013. Molecular Biology and Evolution \nLink: https://academic.oup.com/mbe/article/31/1/48/1050570\n\nAlso, a special thank you to Tom Iliffe for providing some of the photos used in this video.  \nYou can also check out more about anchialine caves at Tom Iliffes cave biology website:\nhttp://www.tamug.edu/cavebiology/index2.html\n\nThe Prokaryo Project seeks to meld hard rock music with microbiology/biological science themes. The songs and videos are meant to be a mix of equal parts music, science and humor. Please take them with a healthy pinch (~0.85g) of sodium chloride and enjoy.\nCheers,\nProkaryo', '2019-07-16 12:03:27', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Prokaryo Band', 'UCtLEx9Vr6ECjG5wahhkXtrQ', 232, 198, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2020-07-28 10:23:04'),
