sion_pages/hubble/science/planet-eater.html', '2017-09-22 19:00:04', 'scishow, scishow space, Space, Science, hank green, astrophysics, astronomy, nasa, new horizons, 2014 MU69, Kuiper Belt, OSIRIS-REx, Bennu, WASP-12b, Hubble Space Telescope, exoplanets, solar system, space news, spacecraft', NULL, 'en', 'SciShow Space', 'UCrMePiHCWG4Vwqv3t7W9EFg', 328, 579664, 14607, 210, 478, 0, 0, '2020-07-31 18:37:18'),
